[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Global pollution** | Content script adds a `<style>` element to `document.head` with `#ielts-content-styles` id | Minimal ‚Äî single style element |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Concern | Current State | Assessment |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Shadow DOM** | Not used ‚Äî uses `all: initial` CSS reset on `.ielts-toolbar`, `.ielts-dict-panel`, `.ielts-ai-panel`, `.ielts-toast` | Medium risk ‚Äî `all: initial` is aggressive but scoped |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **CSS isolation** | Uses `--ielts-*` prefixed variables to avoid host page conflicts | Good |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Event listener cleanup** | No cleanup mechanism when extension is disabled/removed | Medium |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **MutationObserver for dynamic pages** | Highlight engine uses `TreeWalker` on each call ‚Äî no MutationObserver for dynamic content | Medium |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Highlight safety** | Skips `script`, `style`, `iframe`, `svg`, `noscript`, `textarea`, `input`, `select`, `hidden` elements, and `contentEditable` | Good |
[2026-07-05T16:01:22.317Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Max text nodes limit** | 10,000 node limit prevents performance issues on large pages | Good |
